---
description: 
globs: 
alwaysApply: true
---
<rule>
  <meta>
    <title>Git Version Control Standards</title>
    <description>Git 版本控制和協作開發規範，確保代碼品質和團隊協作效率</description>
    <created-at utc-timestamp="1738022400">2025-01-28, 08:00 AM UTC+8</created-at>
    <last-updated-at utc-timestamp="1738022400">2025-01-28, 08:00 AM UTC+8</last-updated-at>
    <applies-to>
      <file-matcher glob="**/*">All files in the project</file-matcher>
      <action-matcher action="git-commit">Triggered when making git commits</action-matcher>
      <action-matcher action="git-push">Triggered when pushing to remote repository</action-matcher>
      <action-matcher action="git-merge">Triggered during merge operations</action-matcher>
    </applies-to>
  </meta>
  <requirements>
    <non-negotiable priority="critical">
      <description>絕對禁止將 .cursor/ 目錄及其內容上傳到 GitHub，這些檔案僅供本地開發使用。</description>
      <examples>
        <example title="Cursor Directory Exclusion">
          <correct-example title="Proper .gitignore configuration" conditions="Setting up repository" expected-result="Cursor files excluded from version control" correctness-criteria="Includes .cursor/ in .gitignore and never commits these files"><![CDATA[# .gitignore 內容
.cursor/
.cursor/**/*
*.mdc

# 確保規則檔案不被追蹤
git rm -r --cached .cursor/
git commit -m "Remove .cursor directory from tracking"]]></correct-example>
          <incorrect-example title="Accidentally committing cursor files" conditions="Making commits without proper .gitignore" expected-result="Clean repository without cursor files" incorrectness-criteria="Commits .cursor/ directory or .mdc files to repository"><![CDATA[git add .
git commit -m "Update project"
# 錯誤：包含了 .cursor/rules/*.mdc 檔案]]></incorrect-example>
        </example>
      </examples>
    </non-negotiable>
    <non-negotiable priority="critical">
      <description>嚴格遵守 GitHub 15 檔案架構限制，不得超出指定的檔案結構。</description>
      <examples>
        <example title="File Structure Compliance">
          <correct-example title="Compliant file structure" conditions="Adding new files to repository" expected-result="Repository within 15-file limit" correctness-criteria="Only includes approved files within the defined structure"><![CDATA[✅ 允許的檔案結構：
根目錄: server.js, package.json, package-lock.json, zeabur.yaml
public/: index.html, teacher-dashboard.html, config.html, css/styles.css, favicon.ico
public/js/: ai-assistant.js, chat.js, conflict.js, editor.js, ui.js, websocket.js

總計：15 個檔案]]></correct-example>
          <incorrect-example title="Exceeding file limit" conditions="Adding unauthorized files" expected-result="Repository within 15-file limit" incorrectness-criteria="Adds files beyond the approved structure"><![CDATA[❌ 禁止添加：
README.md, CHANGELOG.md, CONTRIBUTING.md
.env, .env.example, Dockerfile
docs/, tests/, src/ 等額外目錄]]></incorrect-example>
        </example>
      </examples>
    </non-negotiable>
    <requirement priority="high">
      <description>使用語義化的 commit 訊息格式，包含類型、範圍和繁體中文描述。</description>
      <examples>
        <example title="Commit Message Format">
          <correct-example title="Semantic commit messages" conditions="Making commits" expected-result="Clear, descriptive commit history" correctness-criteria="Uses conventional commit format with Traditional Chinese descriptions"><![CDATA[feat(ai): 新增 AI 助教代碼分析功能
fix(websocket): 修復連線中斷問題
perf(server): 優化 WebSocket 消息處理性能
docs(readme): 更新部署說明文檔
style(ui): 改善響應式設計和按鈕樣式
refactor(backend): 重構用戶管理邏輯
test(ai): 添加 AI 功能單元測試]]></correct-example>
          <incorrect-example title="Poor commit messages" conditions="Making commits" expected-result="Clear commit history" incorrectness-criteria="Uses vague or non-descriptive commit messages"><![CDATA[git commit -m "update"
git commit -m "fix bug"
git commit -m "changes"
git commit -m "wip"]]></incorrect-example>
        </example>
      </examples>
    </requirement>
    <requirement priority="high">
      <description>每次 push 前必須進行本地測試，確保功能正常運作且不破壞現有功能。</description>
      <examples>
        <example title="Pre-push Testing">
          <correct-example title="Complete testing workflow" conditions="Before pushing changes" expected-result="Verified working code" correctness-criteria="Tests all affected functionality and verifies no regressions"><![CDATA[# 推送前檢查清單
1. 本地測試服務器啟動：npm start
2. 測試核心功能：
   - WebSocket 連線
   - AI 助教功能
   - 多人協作
   - 教師監控
3. 檢查控制台錯誤
4. 驗證響應式設計
5. 確認無 linting 錯誤

# 測試通過後推送
git push origin main]]></correct-example>
          <incorrect-example title="Pushing without testing" conditions="Making changes and pushing immediately" expected-result="Verified working code" incorrectness-criteria="Pushes code without local testing or verification"><![CDATA[git add .
git commit -m "feat: 新功能"
git push origin main
# 沒有本地測試，可能破壞生產環境]]></incorrect-example>
        </example>
      </examples>
    </requirement>
    <requirement priority="medium">
      <description>使用分支策略進行功能開發，主分支保持穩定狀態。</description>
      <examples>
        <example title="Branch Strategy">
          <correct-example title="Feature branch workflow" conditions="Developing new features" expected-result="Stable main branch with clean feature development" correctness-criteria="Uses feature branches and merges only tested code"><![CDATA[# 創建功能分支
git checkout -b feature/ai-improvement
git commit -m "feat(ai): 改善 AI 回應速度"

# 測試完成後合併
git checkout main
git merge feature/ai-improvement
git push origin main

# 清理分支
git branch -d feature/ai-improvement]]></correct-example>
          <incorrect-example title="Direct main branch development" conditions="Developing features" expected-result="Stable main branch" incorrectness-criteria="Makes changes directly on main branch without testing"><![CDATA[# 直接在 main 分支開發
git checkout main
git commit -m "嘗試新功能"
git push origin main
# 可能導致主分支不穩定]]></incorrect-example>
        </example>
      </examples>
    </requirement>
    <requirement priority="medium">
      <description>定期更新 Debug 記錄檔案，記錄重要的修復和改進過程。</description>
      <examples>
        <example title="Debug Documentation">
          <correct-example title="Comprehensive debug records" conditions="After fixing issues" expected-result="Updated debug documentation" correctness-criteria="Updates corresponding _debug.mdc files with complete information"><![CDATA[# 修復後更新 Debug 記錄
1. 更新 .cursor/debug/websocket_debug.mdc
2. 記錄問題原因和解決方案
3. 添加預防措施
4. 提交 Debug 記錄更新

git add .cursor/debug/websocket_debug.mdc
git commit -m "docs(debug): 更新 WebSocket 連線問題 Debug 記錄"]]></correct-example>
          <incorrect-example title="Missing debug documentation" conditions="After fixing issues" expected-result="Updated debug documentation" incorrectness-criteria="Fixes issues without updating debug records"><![CDATA[# 修復問題但沒有記錄
git commit -m "fix: 修復 WebSocket 問題"
# 沒有更新對應的 Debug 記錄檔案]]></incorrect-example>
        </example>
      </examples>
    </requirement>
  </requirements>
  <grammar>
    <grammar-entry title="Commit Message Format">
      <pattern description="Conventional commit format with Traditional Chinese">^(feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|perf|test|chore)(\(.+\))?: .+$</pattern>
      <example description="Valid commit message">feat(ai): 新增 AI 助教代碼分析功能</example>
    </grammar-entry>
    <grammar-entry title="Branch Naming Convention">
      <pattern description="Feature branch naming">^(feature|bugfix|hotfix)\/[a-z0-9-]+$</pattern>
      <example description="Valid branch name">feature/ai-improvement</example>
    </grammar-entry>
    <grammar-entry title="Forbidden File Patterns">
      <pattern description="Files that should never be committed">^\.cursor\/.*|.*\.mdc$|README\.md$|\.env.*$</pattern>
      <example description="Forbidden files">.cursor/rules/user_rules.mdc, README.md, .env</example>
    </grammar-entry>
  </grammar>
  <context description="Git workflow and collaboration guidelines">
    這些 Git 規範確保了代碼庫的整潔性和團隊協作的效率。通過嚴格的檔案結構限制和 .cursor/ 目錄排除，保持了 GitHub 倉庫的專業性。語義化的 commit 訊息和分支策略提高了版本控制的可讀性和可維護性。每次推送前的測試要求確保了代碼品質，而 Debug 記錄的維護則有助於知識積累和問題追蹤。
  </context>
  <references>
    <reference as="dependency" href=".cursor/rules/rules.mdc" reason="Follows standard rule format">Base rule format definition</reference>
    <reference as="context" href=".cursor/rules/user_rules.mdc" reason="Related development standards">Universal development standards</reference>
    <reference as="context" href=".cursor/rules/GITHUB_RULES.mdc" reason="Related GitHub guidelines">GitHub upload and structure rules</reference>
  </references>
</rule>
